{"tid":1245222,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Gundam G Generation 懷舊game","createTime":"2019-06-20T08:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T11:30:06.000Z","uid":92324,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f9c75c4375b26f3173b10b163f603b09d6dd4294","tid":1245222,"uid":92324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"有無人玩過<br />\n好懷念<br />\n細個第一個接觸既高達game就係G gen advance<br />\n亦係因為咁愛上左高達呢個系列<br />\n第一關希羅路過就打爆 seed左既基拉<br />\n跟住去到後尾用閃光高達光之劍 超屈機既道門卡遜<br />\n再有阿寶與馬沙既恩怨<br />\n仲要唔識日文一路以為馬沙加入我軍淨係可以做艦長而無得渣沙剎比咁On9 （過幾年重玩睇攻略先知）<br />\n同埋基拉打到好後期先有得用自由高達<br />\n最後仲有隻9999血既大佬 要殺4,5次先死既白色MA<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gQB5NM3DZ0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgQB5NM3DZ0Q&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=6eaf7b12\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gQB5NM3DZ0Q</a><br />\n阿寶vs馬沙<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRE3JwpXp0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCRE3JwpXp0c&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=504de2cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CRE3JwpXp0c</a><br />\n基拉爆seed 打爆X高達果兩兄弟 但之後比希羅路過一下打爆左<br />\n<br />\n跟住係唔知幾多年後 3ds已經出左既年代 先係網上知道原來有續集<br />\nG gen DS 果時仲讀緊中學 特登存左好耐錢先至夠錢買一部2手NDS去玩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8UEIMDOL550\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8UEIMDOL550&d=cvYurzZEI7gK%2Fp8SijS8D1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=050273a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8UEIMDOL550</a><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日同朋友傾舊game<br />\n發覺宜家有好多新game都唔及舊game好玩<br />\n唔知係情懷定真係舊GAME好玩D<br />\n到宜家都唔係好明 點解宜家g gen系列打交一定要出到好似機戰咁<br />\n開招技 1打1 睇完招技就算<br />\n每次玩新版g gen 都係一開頭好玩 跟住就係重復又重復<br />\n點解唔可以用番好似g gen advance 同DS咁既system<br />\n然後每個故事與每個故事之間既劇情又唔會有關聯<br />\n但係 advance同 DS 每個角色都有互動<br />\n就好似基拉爆seed打X高達兩兄弟咁 希羅路過會打爆基拉咁<br />\n<br />\n有無人玩過呢兩隻game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec9caa956e2ae443e10f40decdf8c9a2ba30050","tid":1245222,"uid":31414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:29:39.000Z","msg":"細個玩唔知咁多隱藏野<br />\n大個先知有<br />\n有金色扔石渣古 最記得<br />\n同埋有神盾冇正義"},{"pid":"52c59b9a3e14f83db97ea079de2a5ce87c458592","tid":1245222,"uid":233316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"WS版獨眼高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596a436f374c62a35d8f7ddec49db4c4e00d7175","tid":1245222,"uid":116197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"52c59b9a3e14f83db97ea079de2a5ce87c458592","tid":1245222,"uid":233316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:30:49.000Z","msg":"WS版獨眼高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"Ez8 H.M.C/H.A.C<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8b806b2f7f5c8cade49deaaee43f88e4c58711","tid":1245222,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"G Generation Gather Beat<br />\nWonderSwan既"},{"pid":"65c8814d2bc4d6b4d4333eea1ab5430cba7fd0dd","tid":1245222,"uid":116197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9c75c4375b26f3173b10b163f603b09d6dd4294","tid":1245222,"uid":92324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci